130703.name: Fertilizers indicators - Nutrient nitrogen N (total) - 3102 - Use per area of cropland - 5159 - kg/ha
130703.description: The data describe the use of chemical and mineral fertilizers per area of cropland (which corresponds to the sum of arable land and permanent crops) at national, regional, and global level in a time series from 2002 to 2017

source.name: Agri-Environmental Indicators: Fertilizers indicators
source.dataPublishedBy: Food and Agriculture Organization of the United Nations (FAO) (2020)
source.dataPublisherSource: FAOSTAT Inputs / Fertilizers by Nutrient, and FAOSTAT Inputs / Land Use
source.additionalInfo: The indicator is defined as the annual agricultural use of nutrient Nitrogen N (total), nutrient Phosphate P2O5 (total), and nutrient K2O (total) divided by area of croplands (arable and permanent crops).
